Here's my suggestions, they are just my opinions and what I would do. Thought I'd give some advice :D

First, I see you have a windblade. How much do they go for on your server? On mine, they go for 70k. I would sell the windblade, and either get a War Marshall's Bladed Staff or even a Tae Ew Two Hand Sword, or for a more affordable version of Windblade, Heavy Windrider's Lance ... I'm using the Lance because the ratio is comparable to the Windblade.

Windblade has a 1.14 ratio, Heavy Windriders Lance has a 1.13 ratio, war marshalls bladed staff is 1.11. So really go with whichever is cheapest to help you get upgrades.

Now, if you do decide to sell the windblade, and get say either the Lance or the WMBS, first thing I would do is get rid of those rings. Replace them with Valorium rings of gallantry, or one Ring of Flowing Slime and one Valorium. Get rid of the Oplulant earring of ken, and get a mosquito leg earring if you cant affrod Bloodmetal Earring of Engagement. Upgrading that ear and your fingers would give you a nice boost.

Replace your lesser wrist with another Underfoot Platemail Bracer.

Shoulders - Barbed Dragonscale would be the best. Once you have the extra cash, go for Chokidai Hide Pauldrons.

Replace neck with Clattering Bone Necklace. 

You might be running out of cash by now, or close to it. Start saving up for better upgrades. One thing I would worry about once I get the above mentioned taken care if, is to replace your belt with Soulscream belt, which is 31% haste, and after that, go with Kylong Darkmail Gaunts to replace your SCHW.

thats really it ... the bad thing about being or nearing close to 60, you'll have to invest ALOT of plat in your char, especially if you're a tank. this past month alone I've spent over 200k on ornate for my paladin. My paladin's magelo is included in my sig, have a look at it, and you can see some of the items I've mentioned.

